00:04:39,900 --> 00:04:41,350
are the elements that are going to work?

103
00:04:41,350 --> 00:04:43,250
What are the elements that I like?

104
00:04:43,250 --> 00:04:46,000
So after I've planned it, I do a run-through.

105
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:49,640
Then after I do that run-through and it goes 1,000 hours or however-- it

106
00:04:49,640 --> 00:04:52,320
