107
00:04:52,320 --> 00:04:53,720
down and I reflect.

108
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:57,620
OK, what happened there?

109
00:04:57,620 --> 00:04:58,890
What did I like talking about?

110
00:04:58,890 --> 00:05:00,640
What didn't I like talking about?

111
00:05:00,640 --> 00:05:04,070
When I was talking through it, was I like, I am BS-ing at the moment.

112
00:05:04,070 --> 00:05:05,510
Thankfully no one's around.

113
00:05:05,510 --> 00:05:07,190
This sounds awful.

114
00:05:07,190 --> 00:05:12,010
So I'm trying to think about, what are the big things going on in the speech?

115
00:05:12,010 --> 00:05:14,370
After I'm done with that reflection, I start making revisions.

116
00:05:14,370 --> 00:05:18,260
I jump back into that massive outline document.

117
00:05:18,260 --> 00:05:19,890
And I'm making big changes.

118
00:05:19,890 --> 00:05:22,060
I'm going in, and I'm thinking you know what?

119
00:05:22,060 --> 00:05:24,620
That entire second half of the speech needs to go.

