00:05:24,620 --> 00:05:27,460
Or these goals that I had for the audience?

121
00:05:27,460 --> 00:05:29,950
I need to change these because they're not going to be doable in the time

122
00:05:29,950 --> 00:05:30,630
that I have.

123
00:05:30,630 --> 00:05:36,020
